				\begin{document}$$x{\mathrm{Li}} + {\mathrm{Mn}}^{\mathrm{IV}}{\mathrm{O}}_2 \to {\mathrm{Li}}_x{\mathrm{Mn}}^{\mathrm{III}}{\mathrm{O}}_2.$$\end{document}xLi+MnIVO2→LixMnIIIO2.
